cos for the first time
I had the thought

1053
00:56:37,600 --> 00:56:41,115
that in a very, very strange way,
you got a sweet face.

1054
00:56:41,200 --> 00:56:44,909
It's off-beat
in a kind of bizarre...you know.

1055
00:56:45,000 --> 00:56:48,310
I don't know how to explain it
exactly, but it's...

1056
00:56:48,400 --> 00:56:49,753
it's right up there.

1057
00:56:49,840 --> 00:56:52,752
- What d'you mean?
- It's a compliment, May,

1058
00:56:52,840 --> 00:56:54,831
I'm trying to say a nice thing.

1059
00:56:54,920 --> 00:56:57,195
Cos you being a relative of Frenchy

1060
