There's no doubt about it,
burgundy really goes to my head.

1067
00:57:21,440 --> 00:57:23,510
What did you want to talk about?

1068
00:57:25,400 --> 00:57:27,072
I've, um...

1069
00:57:27,160 --> 00:57:30,072
