a little present for you.

1070
00:57:30,160 --> 00:57:31,513
- For me?
- Yeah.

1071
00:57:31,600 --> 00:57:34,034
- Here.
- Oh...pretty...

1072
00:57:34,120 --> 00:57:36,509
I love leather books.

1073
00:57:36,600 --> 00:57:40,229
Oh, Pygmalion.
I love that story, David.

1074
00:57:40,320 --> 00:57:42,550
There's a little inscription.

1075
00:57:42,640 --> 00:57:44,358
"To my favourite Eliza,

1076
00:57:44,440 --> 00:57:47,318
