1077
00:57:47,400 --> 00:57:49,834
- I got a confession to make.
- What?

1078
00:57:49,920 --> 00:57:51,672
I got you a present too.

1079
00:57:51,760 --> 00:57:54,035
Oh, no, you didn't have to do that.

