1088
00:58:16,200 --> 00:58:17,872
I-I'm embarrassed.

1089
00:58:17,960 --> 00:58:19,598
Don't take up smoking,

1090
00:58:19,680 --> 00:58:23,434
but if it's good enough for
the Duke of Windsor, right?

1091
00:58:23,520 --> 00:58:25,556
Well, I'm really overwhelmed

1092
00:58:25,640 --> 00:58:29,076
and my little Bernard Shaw
is so insignificant...

1093
00:58:29,160 --> 00:58:30,957
No.

1094
00:58:31,040 --> 00:58:32,439
But you see I just...

1095
00:58:32,520 --> 00:58:36,638
I just wanted you to know how
unbelievably proud I am of you.

1096
00:58:36,720 --> 00:58:39,029
David, this is not insignificant.

1097
00:58:39,120 --> 00:58:41,998
Maybe I'm talking
out of turn here but...

1098
00:58:42,080 --> 00:58:45,789
you've just
developed so much and I...

1099
00:58:45,880 --> 00:58:47,871
I just feel that you belong

1100
00:58:47,960 --> 00:58:51,191
in a world of society
and high culture now.

1101
00:58:51,280 --> 00:58:55,068
